summary: This mod adds a very small cave to skyrim. Inside the cave is a Trash bin
descriptionHtml:
This mod puts a very small cave outside of Dawnstar that contains a trash bin that I made in Maya. Download this for a quick laugh or if your looking to give feedback to a novice modder! Thanks in advance for all your kind (or mean) words!

If you want to find your Trash bin, look around Dawnstar.... Or if you like cheating, just coc trashbincave....

Installation
Place the files in your data folder, or make a FOMOD
author: Bradzy
